headline: Qorvo (QRVO) Surpasses Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Qorvo (QRVO) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +48.39% and +5.69%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
